    changesets from the stable-queue branch:
    + a631be (PA_SINK_INPUT_IS_LINKED typo fix)
    + e8cb96 ('Desktop Speaker' handling)
    + 7d6bab ('Shared Mic/Line in', 'Analog Source' handling)
